page.title: 17MY SPARE TIME BY DAMIAN
page.content: In my spare time I like to do a lot of things. I like to go birdwatching because I am interested in recognising and observing birds and I hope to be an expert. I also like to do martial arts so that I can look after myself if I ever get into trouble. I like to draw and I am quite good at drawing birds and people and I like drawing funny pictures. I can water ski but I don't do it all that often. I also go weight lifting and I like keeping fit. I have my own home computer and I programme games on it.
